         <abstract id="aspace_10b1a83290ffd0be5e03d6beecd1939c">Detailed and substantive quarterly letters and writings document the missionary work of Harman V. S. Peeke and his wife Vesta G. Peeke. The Peekes were missionaries in Japan from 1893 to 1929, serving under the Reformed Church in America.</abstract>
